**Ready to deploy?**
1. Update Google OAuth redirect URI (see GOOGLE_OAUTH_SETUP.md Step 7)
2. Set all environment variables above
3. Run `git push heroku main`
4. Visit https://portugal2026-7f6200f7237c.herokuapp.com/
